UltraJSON is a fast and extendable JSON encoder and decoder written in pure C

Python bindings are available as the module ujson with the methods decode and encode

Preliminary benchmarks:

Python 2.6.6 (r266:84297, Aug 24 2010, 18:46:32) [MSC v.1500 32 bit (Intel)]
OS Version: 6.1.7601 Service Pack 1 Build 7601
System Type: x64-based PC
Processor: Intel(R) Core(TM)2 Quad CPU Q9550 @ 2.83GHz 2.83 GHz
Total Physical Memory: 8191 MB

Array with 256 utf-8 strings:
ujson encode      : 1209.93638 calls/sec
simplejson encode : 1029.32459 calls/sec
cjson encode      : 1046.56274 calls/sec

ujson decode      : 1229.74353 calls/sec
cjson decode      : 492.81162 calls/sec
simplejson decode : 269.74984 calls/sec

Medium complex object:
ujson encode      : 10876.64977 calls/sec
simplejson encode : 2547.77450 calls/sec
cjson encode      : 2038.08711 calls/sec

ujson decode      : 7252.82183 calls/sec
cjson decode      : 3572.54022 calls/sec
simplejson decode : 3570.86388 calls/sec

Array with 256 strings:
ujson encode      : 15082.27630 calls/sec
simplejson encode : 15705.86723 calls/sec
cjson encode      : 6392.64500 calls/sec

ujson decode      : 26092.70181 calls/sec
cjson decode      : 16451.40404 calls/sec
simplejson decode : 21206.28568 calls/sec

Array with 256 doubles:
ujson encode      : 27056.81321 calls/sec
simplejson encode : 2047.82538 calls/sec
cjson encode      : 2140.64782 calls/sec

ujson decode      : 28450.97547 calls/sec
cjson decode      : 4129.60953 calls/sec
simplejson decode : 4449.80696 calls/sec

Array with 256 True values:
ujson encode      : 96848.26139 calls/sec
simplejson encode : 34533.60105 calls/sec
cjson encode      : 47166.65394 calls/sec

ujson decode      : 98709.08156 calls/sec
cjson decode      : 58051.89361 calls/sec
simplejson decode : 75504.02214 calls/sec

Array with 256 dict{string, int} pairs:
ujson encode      : 14758.79310 calls/sec
simplejson encode : 3856.79997 calls/sec
cjson encode      : 3022.20674 calls/sec

ujson decode      : 13009.36370 calls/sec
cjson decode      : 7898.21308 calls/sec
simplejson decode : 7145.05462 calls/sec

Dict with 256 arrays with 256 dict{string, int} pairs:
ujson encode      : 14593.93987 calls/sec
simplejson encode : 3824.16247 calls/sec
cjson encode      : 3355.01006 calls/sec

ujson decode      : 12849.49847 calls/sec
cjson decode      : 7868.87442 calls/sec
simplejson decode : 6994.46663 calls/sec

See (python/benchmark.py) for further information.

NOTE: These benchmarks are preliminary! 

